      '<div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" style="margin-bottom: 4px"><defs/><title>messages-bubble-square-menu</title><path d="M23.5 17a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-11l-4 4V18h-6a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1V3a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h21a1 1 0 0 1 1 1Z" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1"/><path x1="9.5" y1="7" x2="18.5" y2="7" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.5 7L18.5 7" stroke-width="1"/><path x1="9.5" y1="12" x2="18.5" y2="12" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.5 12L18.5 12" stroke-width="1"/><path x1="5.5" y1="7" x2="6.5" y2="7" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.5 7L6.5 7" stroke-width="1"/><path x1="5.5" y1="12" x2="6.5" y2="12" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.5 12L6.5 12" stroke-width="1"/></svg><h2 class="Text-ds Text-ds--body-3 Text-ds--left" style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 8px; margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 8px">Feedback</h2></div>';
    customFeedbackButton.addEventListener("click", function () {
      const neb_status = KAMPYLE_ONSITE_SDK.loadForm(38228);

      if (neb_status === true) {
        KAMPYLE_ONSITE_SDK.showForm(38228);
        customFeedbackButton.style.opacity = 0;
      }
    });

    document.body.appendChild(customFeedbackButton);
    document.addEventListener("scroll", throttleScrollEvents);

    window.addEventListener("neb_displayClosed", function (event) {
      customFeedbackButton.style.opacity = 1;
    });
  }
}

window.throttleScrollEvents = () => {
  var currentScrollPos = window.pageYOffset;

  if (!ticking) {
    window.requestAnimationFrame(function () {
      customFeedbackButtonOnScroll(currentScrollPos);
      ticking = false;
    });

    ticking = true;
  }
}

window.customFeedbackButtonOnScroll = (currentScrollPos) => {
  var limit = Math.max(
    document.body.scrollHeight,
    document.body.offsetHeight,
    document.documentElement.clientHeight,
    document.documentElement.scrollHeight,
    document.documentElement.offsetHeight
  );

  if (customFeedbackButton !== null) {
    if (lastScrollPosition > currentScrollPos || currentScrollPos < 0) {
      customFeedbackButton.style.right = "0";
    } else {
      if (currentScrollPos > 300 && currentScrollPos <= limit) {
        customFeedbackButton.style.right = "-48px";
      }
    }

    lastScrollPosition = currentScrollPos;
  }
}

 if(  window.location.pathname == '/' || window.location.href.includes( 'shop' ) || window.location.href.includes( 'beautyservices' )  ) {
    window.initKamplyeSDKCheck();
  }
